      public AppointmentOutcomeRecord(String appointmentOutcomeId, String appointmentId, String patientId, String doctorId, String date, String diagnosis, String treatment, String notes)
      Constructs an AppointmentOutcomeRecord with the specified details.
      Parameters:
      appointmentOutcomeId - the unique identifier for the appointment outcome
      appointmentId - the unique identifier for the appointment
      patientId - the unique identifier for the patient
      doctorId - the unique identifier for the doctor
      date - the date of the appointment outcome
      diagnosis - the diagnosis given during the appointment
      treatment - the treatment prescribed during the appointment
      notes - any additional notes related to the appointment outcome

    • fromCSV

      public static AppointmentOutcomeRecord fromCSV(String[] record)
      Creates an AppointmentOutcomeRecord object from a CSV record.
      Parameters:
      record - String array containing the appointment outcome record data in CSV format where: record[0] = Appointment Outcome ID record[1] = Appointment ID record[2] = Patient ID record[3] = Doctor ID record[4] = Date record[5] = Diagnosis record[6] = Treatment record[7] = Notes
      Returns:
      A new AppointmentOutcomeRecord object populated with the CSV data
